-
-## Purpose
-
-This file makes lifecycle behavior explicit. It separates a listed status from a modeled transition.
-
-A status name is not enough. A useful state model must identify:
-
-- entry trigger;
-- exit trigger;
-- actor;
-- visibility;
-- allowed next states;
